layout: layouts/story-brand.njk
title: The Garden
description: How Ferni stays free. A different kind of funding.
permalink: /garden/
---

<main class="garden-page">

  {# Hero #}
  <section class="story-page__hero">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <p class="story-page__eyebrow">The Garden</p>
      <h1 class="story-page__headline">No investors.<br>No paywalls.<br>Just gardeners.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Question #}
  <section class="story-page__section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">Most AI charges $20-50/month.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          We asked a different question:
        </p>
        <p class="story-page__accent">
          What if we just... didn't?
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Model #}
  <section class="story-page__section story-page__section--dark">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">Seeds, not subscriptions.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          Ferni doesn't have investors demanding growth.<br>
          It has a community planting seeds.
        </p>
        <p class="story-page__text story-page__text--muted">
          When people who can afford to give a little do, everyone benefits.
          No paywalls. No premium tiers. No "upgrade to unlock" moments 
          right when you need support most.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Why #}
  <section class="story-page__section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">Gardeners, not customers.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          Contributors aren't buying a product.<br>
          They're nurturing something alive.
        </p>
        <p class="story-page__text story-page__text--muted">
          And free users? They're gardeners too—
          tending to the garden just by showing up.
          Every conversation helps Ferni grow.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Promise #}
  <section class="story-page__section story-page__section--accent">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">When enough people give a little,<br>everyone gets a lot.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          Life coaching shouldn't be a luxury.<br>
          Someone to talk to shouldn't cost $200/session.<br>
          Support at 3am shouldn't require a premium plan.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# CTA #}
  <section class="story-page__section story-page__section--cta">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">Plant a seed.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          If you can, contribute what feels right.<br>
          If you can't, just use Ferni. That's enough.
        </p>
        <div class="story-page__cta">
          <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}?garden=true" class="btn btn--garden btn--lg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="20" height="20">
              <path d="M7 20h10"/><path d="M10 20c5.5-2.5.8-6.4 3-10"/><path d="M9.5 9.4c1.1.8 1.8 2.2 2.3 3.7-2 .4-3.5.4-4.8-.3-1.2-.6-2.3-1.9-3-4.2 2.8-.5 4.4 0 5.5.8z"/><path d="M14.1 6a7 7 0 0 0-1.1 4c1.9-.1 3.3-.6 4.3-1.4 1-1 1.6-2.3 1.7-4.6-2.7.1-4 1-4.9 2z"/>
            </svg>
            Plant a Seed
          </a>
          <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}" class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg">
            Or just begin a conversation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
